name: Tieka_Dalken
content: Tieka Dalken was a Neimoidian female who lived on Cato Neimoidia during the Clone Wars. Unlike most of the planet's residents, Dalken had a high opinion of the Jedi Suljo Warde, for he saved Dalken's and her family's lives during the Galactic Republic's attack on Cato Neimoidia.
